<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <title>New Reply Notification</title>
    <meta
      http-equiv="Content-Type"
      content="text/html; charset=UTF-8"
    />
    <meta
      name="viewport"
      content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"
    />

    <style type="text/css">
      /* Base */
      body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        min-width: 100%;
        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.5;
        background-color: #fafafa;
        color: #222222;
      }
      a {
        color: #000;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
      h1 {
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: 700;
        line-height: 1.25;
        margin-top: 0;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      p {
        margin-top: 0;
        margin-bottom: 18px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Hello <%= name %></h1>
    <p>A new reply has been added to your question in the video <%= title %></p>
    <p>
      Please login to our website to view the reply and continue the discussion
    </p>
    <p>Thank you for being a part of our community</p>
  </body>
</html>
